<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><lyrics>[V1]
 nǐ men yào kāi kěn huāng de, dāng chèn zhe chūn yǔ sā zǐ lì,
 nǐ men yào ná qǐ lián dāo, zhuāng jià yǐ jīng chéng shú, děng dài zhe nǐ,
 jīn rì kuài wèi zhǔ bēn pǎo, xiàn shàng nǐ de lì liàng, zhōng xīn dào dǐ,
 tóng gōng men kuài xìng qǐ! zhǔ yǔ wǒ men tóng zài, qí xīn nǔ lì.</lyrics>
<title>nǐ men yào kāi kěn huāng de 迦南159</title>
<hymn_number>159</hymn_number>
<author>lǚ xiǎo mǐn</author>
